Receita de Carne Moída:
 - 500 g de carne moída
 -1/2 cebola
- 2 colheres (sopa) de óleo
- 2 dentes de alho amassados
-1 colher (sopa) rasa de extrato de tomate
-coentro a gosto
-1 colher (sopa) rasa daqueles temperos completos que já vêm pronto

Modo de Preparo
Em uma panela coloque a carne com o óleo, 1 colher de tempero e o alho
Misture bem e deixe descansar por 5 minutos.
Em seguida bata no liquidificador a cebola e o coentro com 1/2 xícara de água.
Depois despeje tudo na panela da carne junto com o extrato de tomate.
Deixe cozinhar até pegar gosto e a carne ficar no ponto.

This is my second completed run of this game. I'm using a fairly easy route without many difficult tricks.

I made a number of mistakes, including:

- Accidentally falling into the slide on CCM
- Falling into quicksand in SSL

Because I accidentally completed the slide in CCM, I skipped Blast Away the Wall in WF.

Right around the time I started trying the BLJs, my right C button began occasionally producing input when it was not being pressed. Towards the end of the run it failed completely. This is why my camera control is strange on Bowser in the Sky.

There's quite a lot to improve on here. I definitely need to get better at BLJs and Bowser throws. I also need to fix my controller. :)
